Arcana v2.0 is a rewrite of the Arcana v1.0 package by 

Thomas G. Close (Sydney Imaging, The University of Sydney, Sydney, Australia)

In addition, the following persons contributed source code, concepts and documentation to Arcana v1.0.

Francesco Sforazzini (Monash Biomedical Imaging, Monash University, Melbourne, Australia)
Phillip G. D. Ward (Monash Biomedical Imaging, Monash University, Melbourne, Australia)


